snippet: Danaejah Grant scored 17 points and the St. John’s women (12-1) held No. 23 Seton Hall without a field goal for almost the final nine and a half minutes in a 59-50 home win.
abstract: St John's women's college basketball team defeats Seton Hall, 59-50; Notre Dame defeats Florida State, 74-68, in women's college basketball action.
lead_paragraph: Danaejah Grant scored 17 points and the St. John’s women (12-1) held No. 23 Seton Hall without a field goal for almost the final nine and a half minutes in a 59-50 home win.

headline.main: Seton Hall Women Fall to St. John’s
